<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Inkra Data Export Failed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #4F46E5;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4F46E5;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .error-section {
      background: #FEF2F2;
      border-left: 4px solid #EF4444;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .error-section h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #B91C1C;
    }
    .support-section {
      background: #F0F9FF;
      border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #6B7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">Inkra</div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>Data Export Failed</h2>
    
    <p>Hi there,</p>
    
    <p>We encountered an issue while preparing your Inkra data export and were unable to complete the process.</p>

    <div class="error-section">
      <h3>What happened:</h3>
      <p>Our system experienced a technical issue while collecting and packaging your data. This could be due to a temporary server problem or connectivity issue.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="support-section">
      <h3>What we're doing:</h3>
      <p>Our technical team has been automatically notified of this issue. We'll investigate the problem and work to resolve it quickly.</p>
      
      <p>We'll attempt to retry your export automatically, and you should receive another email when it's ready.</p>
    </div>

    <p>If you continue to experience issues with your data export, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@inkra.app">support@inkra.app</a>. Please include the following information in your message:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Your account email: <%= @user.email %></li>
      <li>Time of request: <%= Time.current.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z') %></li>
      <li>This error reference: EXPORT_FAILED_<%= @user.id %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>We apologize for the inconvenience and appreciate your patience while we resolve this issue.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The Inkra Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This notification was sent to <%= @user.email %> regarding your data export request.</p>
    <p>Inkra - Capture your voice, preserve your story</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>